data.description:
Like new! Move - in! Lindenwood Park neighborhood! 1650 sg ft, 6020 Juniata 63139. 40's ranch on a slab, 3 brd, 2 bath, Family room! Remodeled Off street parking. 
Newer kit cabinets, granite, stainless steel appliances, king size peninsula bar. Exceptional kitchen & bathrooms.

Bring your retirement money or inheritance.

V.A. 3% assumable loan to veteran or non-veteran! Loan balance $212,683 est. requires $52,317 cash to assume plus assumption fee and good credit! Price $265,000.

   Sub agent 2.5 % buyers agent 2.5%  transaction brokerage 2.5% 

  Vacant,
 call MLS to show

Ask Listing Broker for E-Z plan for 1 + car attached garage heated or E-Z plan mother - in law quarters with separate entry or Airbnb separare entry, too.
